"i18n:InfoMessage.FeaturesUnavailableForOlderMacOS" = "Some features are unavailable for macOS 10.15 and macOS 11 due to API limitations.";
"i18n:InfoMessage.MacOS10_9Bug" = "There is a bug in macOS 10.9, preventing an input method from accessing its own file panels. Doing so will result in eternal hang-crash of not only the input method but all client apps it tries attached to, requiring SSH connection to this computer to terminate the input method process by executing “killall vChewing”. Due to possible concerns of the same possible issue in macOS 10.10 and 10.11, we completely disabled this feature.";
