"i18n:UserDef.kBasicKeyboardLayout.description" = "Choose the macOS-level basic keyboard layout. Non-QWERTY alphanumerical keyboard layouts are for Pinyin parser only. This option will only affect the appearance of the on-screen-keyboard if the current Mandarin parser is neither (any) pinyin nor dynamically reparsable with different western keyboard layouts (like Eten 26, Hsu, etc.).";
